|3| ^so^ no one ^will^ be drawn aside [or ^deceived^ or ^disturbed^] by these
afflictions. For you yourselves know that to this we are appointed,

# Acts 9:16
# I will show him how much he must suffer for my name."

# Acts 14:22
# strengthening the disciples and encouraging them to remain true to the faith.
