|4| for even when we were with you, we said before [or ^beforehand^ or ^in
advance^] to you that we are about to be afflicted, [or ^persecuted^] as also
it happened, [or ^and so it happened^] and you know. [or ^as you know^]

# 1 Thessalonians 2:14
# For you, brothers and sisters, became imitators of God's churches in Judea,
