|8| because now we live if you stand in ^the^ Lord.

# 1 Corinthians 16:13
# Be on your guard; stand firm in the faith; be courageous; be strong.

|9| For what thanks are we able to return to God concerning you, over all the
joy ^with^ which we rejoice ^because of^ [literally ^by^] you before our God,

# 1 Thessalonians 1:2
# Thanksgiving for the Thessalonians' Faith - We always thank God for all of
